{"books":[{"id":"whb","name":"文汇报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"$和卍!","authors":["冀汸"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":12,"day":25}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"冀汸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——向右转!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向右转!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——时间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向右转!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从美丽的白昼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌天黑地!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——教堂尖端底十字架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向右转!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像痉摩的手足"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转成一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丑恶的卍!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜鲁门在祷告"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他替华尔街的老板们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的祷告!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"S和卍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是帝国主义最后阶段的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并发症，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它已经装饰在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白宫底大门上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它已经贴在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华盛顿和林肯底鼻子上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它已经嵌在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星点红条的国旗上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它已经像花柳病菌一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漩流在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愚蠢的美国人底血液里!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"S走在前面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卐跟在后边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"S走到不列颠王国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"O.K.，好得很，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在不列颠的历史上盖上一记卐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经“骄傲”过的绅士们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就作了美国底奴隶!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"S走到法兰西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"All Right，其正不错，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在法兰西底版图上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盖上一记卐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经“豪华”过的“共和国”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就成了美国底市场和原料供应地!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"S走到那里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卐就跟到那里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"S走到西德，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卐就跟到西德。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好了，希特勒在地下欢呼:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——呵，我底上帝!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Madeln U.S.A.的卐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来和德国造的卐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一式一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有分别!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，流氓们，得意忘形了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再来一个偷天换日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把“联合国”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锁进银行底保险库里，放心大胆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一脚踩在日本人民身上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手攫进朝鲜底心腹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再向新中国伸出舌头，流开口水!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃饱了人肉筵宴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝够了可口可乐糖浆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躺在沙发上打噎放屁的大亨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"们，你们竟忘记了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是中国!这是中国!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们竟忘记了:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个蒋介石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个被你们封为“顶好”的猫脚爪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从你们手上取得了天文数字的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并且拥有希、墨两家嫡传的老牌卐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国人民底铁拳下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样像烂泥巴一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稀哩哗啦地坍场了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们竟忘记了:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民一直团结在共产党底周围"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民一直是毛泽东底战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十年的斗争"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过多少险路，闯过多少难关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对于你们这套流氓派头的Boxing，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老实说，简直毫不在乎!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并且，正告你们，老板们!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一回不是什么买卖，讨价还价"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们该一手，我们就退一步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一定要扭着打，打到底!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到你们从历史底尖端上摔下来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉身碎骨，结束这丑恶的时代——向右转!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向右转!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜鲁门，发昏的总统先生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你还嚎叫一些什么呢?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事实的确对于你们太糟糕:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界在向左转!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向左转!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进!前进!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民站起来了，前进!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"束德人民站起来了，前进!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜在前进!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越南在前进!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"印度尼西亚在前进!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马来亚在前进!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非洲在前进!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴力斯坦也在前进……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方和西方都在前进!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连贵国底“不守秩序”的公民们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也在和平呼吁书上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄严地写下了自己底姓名!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"s和卐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老板们，这不是什么法宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是你们断命的病症!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原子弹或者氢弹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也万万不能起死回生!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我有卐!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有卐!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论你叫得多么狂暴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们决不怕!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它就得永远成为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类史上一个可耻的符号!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我有S!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有S!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论你呼喊得多么甜蜜我们决不要!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们遵从不朽的列宁底指示:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“当我们将来在世界范围内胜利了的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们会在世界几个最大城市的街道上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用金子筑成一些公共厕所”!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五○年十一月十二夜。"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}